661,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:12:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb7fbb0a5f05999b606071681f9b0c530133cea","tid":1438661,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:12:37.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n不分化 不篤灰 不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家記住飲多啲水 天氣熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0f20f9be481ce8c4eddcffda27c7749c41ae0f","tid":1438661,"uid":283157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:13:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c429cdd663b9d064a5b04280154a3d41182091f","tid":1438661,"uid":258416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:14:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9174633c8daf204dcafc0d090b3cddb763a37849","tid":1438661,"uid":48767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:15:41.000Z","msg":"泛民打手又要出動"},{"pid":"f158d6be22630bcf25266e45ea849c1bf9da3df1","tid":1438661,"uid":263973,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fWHbHsV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfWHbHsV.jpg&h=bc85ed9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">請大家認準目標</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 對於D 藍絲廢Post, 一定要冷處理, 愈回應, 佢地愈High (藍絲不是敵人, 藍絲只是唔會醒既豬)<br />\n2. 商家對示威者有敵意, 可以建立罷買黑名單, 支持幫呢D商家宣傳出名, 但要以宣傳主線任務為主<br />\n3. 對住黑社會, 不主動攻擊, 但要識得自保同必要時還拖. 同黑社會合作既警隊係廢既<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>藍絲, 商家, 黑社會,<br />\n都不是我們既目標,<br />\n請記得目標只有一個,<br />\n就係呢個沒有道德既政權</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求, 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港, 時代革命"},{"pid":"ef4a16f6b451373b97038ed412e7128cba2c619c","tid":1438661,"uid":210995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"reply